cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.IT 

The paper discusses the use of edge cloud deployments in 5G cellular networks to enable advanced machine learning applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The paper also discusses the architecture of cellular networks, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the use of data to make predictions, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory).
